data.description: GRANDIOSO! Stunning home located on cul-de-sac in Kipling Estates! 2-story Foyer will welcome you to YOUR new home! 3746 square feet! Formal Living Room and Dining Room! Spectaular gourmet Eat in Kitchen boasts staggered cabinets, island with overhang for seating, built in stainless steel appliances, walk in pantry! Enjoy spacious 2-story Family room with abundance of windows and fireplace! 2 staircases located in foyer and family room (quite the upgrade)! 1st floor Laundry room! Master Bedroom suite features walk in closet (12'x11') with luxury bathroom, dual sink, walk in shower, soaker tub! Bedroom 2 has private full bathroom! Bedrooms 3 and 4 has Jack in Jill bathroom with built in closet organizers! Hardwood floors, Ceiling fans, White trim! Full unfinished basement with rough in! 3 car garage! Concrete driveway! Private backyard backs to walking path, is a 10+, relax on your paver patio, pergola, wrought iron fenced yard. No neighbors behind you! Fully landscaped! Sprinkler system! Clubhouse community, walking trails, splash pad, ponds, clubhouse, pool and workout center! Minooka schools!
